msgid ""
"The  mode of AI QoS, default mode is \"auto\", another mode is  "
"\"manual\",some parameters need to be configured if you choose  "
"\"manual\" mode."
msgstr "AI QoS的模式，默认模式为\"auto\"，另一种模式为\"manual\"，如果选择\"manual\"模式则需要配置一些参数。"

