#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/Ai_QoS_introduction_en.md
msgid ""
"AIV_D2D: high,<br />AIV_H2D: high,<br />SDMA_D2D: high,<br />SDMA_H2D: "
"low,<br />PCIEDMA_H2D: high"
msgstr ""
"AIV_D2D: high,<br />AIV_H2D: high,<br />SDMA_D2D: high,<br />SDMA_H2D: "
"low,<br />PCIEDMA_H2D: high"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/Ai_QoS_introduction_en.md
msgid ""
"Parameters  for \"manual\" mode, determined the QoS priority of different"
" types  of traffic.     <br />The default configuration is the same as "
"\"auto\" mode.     <br />Typical traffic types are as follows for "
"reference:     AIV_D2D: AIV-based  Device-to-Device communication, such "
"as dispatch and combine.<br /> AIV_H2D: AIV-based  Operator Delivery.<br "
"/> SDMA_D2D: SDMA-based  Device-to-Device communication, such as "
"Allreduce and Allgather.<br />SDMA_H2D: SDMA-based  Host-to-Device"
"/Device-to-Host communication, such as KVCache offloading and  "
"prefetching.<br />PCIEDMA_H2D: PCIEDMA-based  Operator Delivery.   <br />"
"  You can change the priority of different types of traffic, with  "
"\"high/middle/low\" options available.Due to hardware restrictions,  "
"\"PCIEDMA_H2D\" only supports  \"high/low\" priority."
msgstr ""
"\"manual\"模式的参数，决定不同类型流量的QoS优先级。<br />默认配置与\"auto\"模式相同。<br "
"/>典型流量类型如下供参考：AIV_D2D：基于AIV的设备到设备通信，如dispatch和combine。<br "
"/>AIV_H2D：基于AIV的算子下发。<br "
"/>SDMA_D2D：基于SDMA的设备到设备通信，如Allreduce和Allgather。<br "
"/>SDMA_H2D：基于SDMA的主机到设备/设备到主机通信，如KVCache卸载和预取。<br "
"/>PCIEDMA_H2D：基于PCIEDMA的算子下发。<br "
"/>您可以更改不同类型流量的优先级，提供\"high/middle/low\"选项。由于硬件限制，\"PCIEDMA_H2D\"仅支持\"high/low\"优先级。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/Ai_QoS_introduction_en.md:65
msgid "**How to disable AI QoS**:"
msgstr "**如何禁用AI QoS**："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/Ai_QoS_introduction_en.md:71
msgid ""
"​The command for disabling the AI QoS feature on the UB Switch will be "
"printed on the screen. Please log in to the UB Switch and execute the "
"command printed on the screen to complete the feature disabling."
msgstr "​禁用UB交换机上AI QoS特性的命令将打印在屏幕上。请登录UB交换机并执行屏幕上打印的命令以完成特性禁用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/Ai_QoS_introduction_en.md:73
msgid "Usage Constraints"
msgstr "使用约束"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/Ai_QoS_introduction_en.md:75
msgid ""
"​Due to underlying driver limitations, the QoS configurations for AIV_H2D"
" and AIV_D2D do not take effect currently. Once the required adaptation "
"capabilities are added in a future driver release, this feature will be "
"delivered through a module upgrade."
msgstr "​由于底层驱动限制，AIV_H2D和AIV_D2D的QoS配置当前不生效。一旦未来驱动版本中添加了所需的适配能力，此特性将通过模块升级交付。"

